snippet.title: Returnal - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get another look at Returnal in this latest trailer for the upcoming PlayStation 5 exclusive.

Join ASTRA Scout Selene and survive the shifting landscape of Atropos when Returnal arrives on April 30, 2021 for PlayStation 5.

#IGN #Gaming #PS5
